=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.2 ***
=====================================================================

The program now is able to evaluate the Kinetic Energy Density
in Momentum Space.
The implementation required some changes in the main program and
in the help menu.

=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.1 ***
=====================================================================

Some changes to the help menu and support for long command line
options (e.g. --help, and --version).

=====================================================================
*** Version 1.0.0 ***
=====================================================================

First release of the program.

